data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: Marines with 2nd Reconnaissance Battalion, 2nd Marine Division, conducted fast rope insertion and close quarter training at the military operations on urban terrain facility aboard Marine Corps Base Camp Lejeune, N.C., Nov. 19 to 21, 2014. The exercise integrated the reconnaissance Marines and the helicopter pilots requiring the same level of communication and cooperation they would use during combat operations to ensure realism and effective training.
